<section class="what-is">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>What is Breachwalker?</h2>
    <p>
      Breachwalker is a web-first expedition survival game from Benum Labs. You
      stand on the surface hold, select a rift from the ledger, and breach inward
      — managing stamina, fighting through procedurally derived space, and
      deciding when to extract loot to your vault.
    </p>
    <p>
      Rifts are seeded from Bitcoin's public on-chain history, so two catalog
      entries can feel radically different in danger and scale. The closed alpha
      tests whether that loop is worth returning to before marketplace trade and
      item NFTs on Base join the picture.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

